high_descs: Turn around and go to the bathtub
Pick up the dirty red rag that is on the left
Turn around and then go to the sink that is on your right
Place the rag into the sink and turn on the water to rinse the rag. Then turn off the water and pick up the cleaned rag
Turn around and head to the toilet, make a left and face the bathtub
Place the clean red rag in the bathtub to the right of the soap and left of the dirty red rag.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean rag in a bathtub

high_descs: Turn around to face the white tub.
Pick up the red towel from inside the tub on the left side.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the towel in the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around and return to the tub on the left side.
Put the rinsed towel in between the bar of soap and the other towel.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed towel in a tub.

high_descs: grab the cloth on the left
put the cloth in the sink, wash the cloth with water, take the cloth out
put the cloth back in the tub
anns.task_desc: wash the cloth from the tub, put it back in the tub
